<h1 id="interpret" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#interpret" aria-hidden="true">#</a> interpret</h1>
<p><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/interpret" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="http://img.shields.io/npm/v/interpret.svg" alt="NPM version"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/interpret" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="http://img.shields.io/npm/dm/interpret.svg" alt="Downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://travis-ci.org/gulpjs/interpret" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="http://img.shields.io/travis/gulpjs/interpret.svg?label=travis-ci" alt="Travis Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://ci.appveyor.com/project/gulpjs/interpret" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/appveyor/ci/gulpjs/interpret.svg?label=appveyor" alt="AppVeyor Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://coveralls.io/r/gulpjs/interpret" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="http://img.shields.io/coveralls/gulpjs/interpret/master.svg" alt="Coveralls Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://gitter.im/gulpjs/gulp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://badges.gitter.im/gulpjs/gulp.svg" alt="Gitter chat"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
<p>A dictionary of file extensions and associated module loaders.</p>
<h2 id="what-is-it" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#what-is-it" aria-hidden="true">#</a> What is it</h2>
<p>This is used by <a href="http://github.com/tkellen/node-liftoff" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Liftoff<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> to automatically require dependencies for configuration files, and by <a href="http://github.com/tkellen/node-rechoir" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">rechoir<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> for registering module loaders.</p>
<h2 id="api" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#api" aria-hidden="true">#</a> API</h2>
<h3 id="extensions" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#extensions" aria-hidden="true">#</a> extensions</h3>
<p>Map file types to modules which provide a <a href="http://nodejs.org/api/globals.html#globals_require_extensions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">require.extensions<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> loader.</p>
